    <h2 class="mt-5 text-[24px] font-semibold">Future</h2>
    <p class="mt-4">We’re looking to open source our initial code in coming weeks to aid in transparency and collaboration with the developer community. As the Incubator for AI scales its initial team, we will be developing atop the features above with User oriented design and AI safety at the core.</p>
    <p class="mt-4">A few of the potential growth areas include:</p>
